South African rapper Riky Rick has died. AFP/Miguel Medina JOHANNESBURG - Much-loved local rapper Riky Rick will be buried next Tuesday. The multi-award-winning rapper died on Wednesday morning. READ: Riky Rick dies aged 34 Rikhado Muziwendlovu Makhado was 34 years old. The funeral will take place at a private ceremony in Johannesburg and the service will be live-streamed. READ: Fans, industry peers shocked by Riky Rick's death Rick is survived by his wife and two children. Close friends and family will gather for a special Tribute Celebration on Friday. His family says they have been overwhelmed by the support it's received.